YLOPONOM USER GUIDE

1. First start a server
	./server [port] [ip]

2. Connect any number of clients up to 8 to the server at [port] and [ip]
	./yloponom

3. Turn progression will indicate the current player's turn. If a player
can buy a property, a message box will appear. 

4. If the player loses, the game will close to indicate the loss.

5. The last player remaining is the winner.

6. During the turn, a player is free to trade or improve his properties.

7. When done playing, be sure to CTRL+C the server process.

